com.motorola.mod

Class ModProtocol.Protocol

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum
      • com.motorola.mod.ModProtocol.Protocol
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable
    Enclosing class:
    ModProtocol

    public static final class ModProtocol.Protocol
extends Enum
    This class presents the actual greybus protocol id, which the ModProtocol instance is associated with. The Protocol enumeration defined the declared Protocol and their corresponding Protocol ID, which the ModProtocol instance is associated with. While the Protocol enumeration defines all existing greybus protocol and Moto Mod platform added protocols, only the protocols marked as 'supported' are supported in the initial release of the Moto Mod Platform.
